`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Disarm
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * disarm <target>

 Disarm is designed to relieve your opponent of his weapon.  The best possible
chance of disarming occurs when you are skilled in both your own and your
opponent's weapon. Only talented thieves and warriors may learn this skill. It
is dependent on dexterity.

